              "<p class=\"badge blocked\">Blocked - Missing Required Evidence</p>",
              "<h1 class=\"title\">Vendor Evidence Readiness SDK</h1>",
              "<p class=\"subtitle\">AI Development Team Delivery Report for Acme Cloud Services</p>",
              "</section>",
              "<section class=\"panel wide\">",
              "<h2>User Story</h2>",
              "<p>As a procurement reviewer, I want a vendor evidence readiness checker, so that I can see whether a vendor packet has the required documents and unsupported claims before sending it to security review.</p>",
              "</section>",
              "<section class=\"panel wide\">",
              "<h2>AI Development Team Flow</h2>",
